data.description: Welcome home to this beautifully updated GEM! With 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this home is perfect for someone looking for comfort AND style. The sunken living room is sure to be your favorite spot to unwind and relax. With its spacious layout, you'll have no problem arranging furniture and making it your own. Down the hall you’ll be greeted by a spacious primary bedroom and bath complete with a double vanity and his and her closets, getting ready in the morning just got a whole lot more enjoyable. And let's not forget about the updates throughout the entire home! Fixtures, cabinets and hardware just to start… no detail has been overlooked. This home truly combines style and functionality, creating a perfect blend of comfort and sophistication. Out back, you’ll enjoy your private backyard oasis and be surrounded by the calming presence of mature trees. You'll have easy access to schools, shops, and entertainment, making everyday life a breeze. Located just down the road from Fort Cavazos and easy access to Killeen-Fort Hood Regional Airport, you’ll want to call 406 Baumann “home”.
